Story

Once upon a time, In a forest, there lived a Monkey on a tree which was on the banks of the river. In the same forest there lived a Crocodile and his Wife. One day
The Crocodile came upto the banks of the river and restedd under the tree. the kind hearted monkey offered hi som fruits . the crocodile came the next morning for 
more fruits as he loved them.as days passesd by, The crocodile and monkey became good friends.